abstract: Tiger Woods prepares to tee off in the British Open at Muirfield in search of his first major title in 17 starts; he has not won a single title in the past 20 majors after winning six titles in the previous 20-major stretch.
lead_paragraph: Whether because of health, self-confidence or something else, Tiger Woods has not won in the past 20 majors after winning six titles in the previous 20-major span.

headline.main: As Woods Stepped Back, the Field Surged Forward
